<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="123">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Italy. Toscana.</emphasis>
Arcidosso (Grosseto), Stribugliano, lungo la Via del Campo Sportivo (WGS84: 
<geoCoordinate degrees="42.85868" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="1" value="42.85868">42.85868N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="11.47165" direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="1" value="11.47165">11.47165E</geoCoordinate>
), 28 May 2021, 
